sp.p:
You see Kinsman I am som-what bould to call in, and see
how you do, I heard you were safe inough, and I was very glad
on't that it was no worse;

Come, let me tell you, ya're too vnkinde a Kinsman yfaith;
the Captaine louing you so deerely, I, like the Pomwater of his
eye, and you to be so vncomfortable, fie, fie.

Purgatorie? tuh; that word deserues to bee spit vpon;
I wonder that a man of sober toung as you seeme to be, should
haue the folly to beleeue there's such a place.

I, I knew by their shuffling Clubs would be Trumpe;
masse here's the Knaue, and hee can doe any good vppon 'em:
Clubs, clubs, clubs?
